Yeah, I spoke to Prosecutor Yang
on the phone.

17
00:01:16,955 --> 00:01:18,790
He's a professor now.

18
00:01:20,291 --> 00:01:21,209
Are you sure though?

19
00:01:22,043 --> 00:01:24,170
-Yes, I must do this.
-If you can't do it…

20
00:01:24,254 --> 00:01:26,089
I will do it.

21
00:01:26,172 --> 00:01:27,340
You can just study.

22
00:01:31,803 --> 00:01:33,429
A search and seizure warrant?

23
00:01:33,513 --> 00:01:35,723
Do you think
the higher-ups will approve it?

24
00:01:36,432 --> 00:01:37,267
Never.

25
