Hey, are you on the plane?

55
00:03:17,242 --> 00:03:18,076
What?

56
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:20,495
CAFÉ RITA COFFEE

57
00:03:20,578 --> 00:03:22,664
Ko Hyeong-su doesn't trust anyone easily.

58
00:03:22,747 --> 00:03:25,458
Calm Sol A down so she won't give it away.

59
00:03:25,541 --> 00:03:27,460
