72
00:04:21,973 --> 00:04:23,391
I will remember that.

73
00:04:23,474 --> 00:04:24,559
KO HYEONG-SU

74
00:04:24,642 --> 00:04:26,019
ASSEMBLYMAN KO HYEONG-SU

75
00:04:27,270 --> 00:04:29,355
All right, now.
I'm Park Geun-tae, an attorney.

76
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:31,899
