80
00:04:41,326 --> 00:04:42,160
KO HYEONG-SU

81
00:04:42,994 --> 00:04:44,162
Kang Dan, you.

82
00:04:44,954 --> 00:04:46,456
You'll have to pay for this!

83
00:04:46,539 --> 00:04:47,707
Right.

84
