NOTICE

93
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:30,792
What is this?

94
00:05:30,875 --> 00:05:32,085
SPECIAL LECTURE CANCELED

95
00:05:32,168 --> 00:05:33,920
ERICA SHIN'S LECTURE HAS BEEN CANCELED

96
00:05:34,003 --> 00:05:36,672
