285
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,455
Since when?

286
00:16:35,289 --> 00:16:36,915
Yes, I'm leaving now.

287
00:16:37,708 --> 00:16:40,335
I'm headed to the airport now,
so keep an eye on him.

288
00:16:51,430 --> 00:16:53,557
-What's going on?
-I'll get out and check.

289
00:16:55,684 --> 00:16:56,769
Hey.

290
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:59,021
