and enjoy the smooth ride to the precinct?

297
00:17:14,495 --> 00:17:15,329
Let's go.

298
00:17:19,416 --> 00:17:21,752
How do you feel
to have passed the preliminaries?

299
00:17:21,835 --> 00:17:25,339
