379
00:22:12,125 --> 00:22:15,337
Go read the law books
instead of wasting your time like this.

380
00:22:15,420 --> 00:22:16,922
-Jeez.
-If you're going to whine,

381
00:22:17,005 --> 00:22:18,090
do it elsewhere.

382
00:22:30,185 --> 00:22:32,521
