403
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:31,097
You guys pick first.
I'll take what's left over.

404
00:24:32,140 --> 00:24:33,225
You can do anything?

405
00:24:34,684 --> 00:24:37,103
I got the summary
and the closing argument.

406
00:24:37,187 --> 00:24:39,773
